{"tid":1395141,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我想問你地班撚樣憑乜嘢屌達哥？","createTime":"2019-08-01T16:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T06:44:31.000Z","uid":251052,"like":16,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3b21cf5e61b1a97eb00762be468498e6c320d9a4","tid":1395141,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:02:21.000Z","msg":"我想問你地班撚樣憑乜嘢屌達哥？<br />\n逢星期一至五九點半開台打機，<br />\n咁多年黎風雨不改，<br />\n有無問過你地收一分錢呀？<br />\n咁多年黎不辭勞苦，病住沙聲都做直播<br />\n仲記得有次做到開唔到聲提早收台<br />\n呢啲野又有無人記得呀？<br />\n<br />\n因為表態遲左，萬人圍插<br />\n呢個就係你地既答案？<br />\n佔中果時，一句在心中<br />\n之後sleeping dogs黑警mode<br />\n真兄弟一定記得<br />\n<br />\n但係狗登為左捧什麼toy z定乜乜<br />\n係咁踩達哥<br />\n狗登小朋友當道我當佢唔識野<br />\n高登又跟住去反達？<br />\n無撚野呀？<br />\n咁多年兄弟比班𡃁仔講兩句話反就反？<br />\n做兄弟唔係咁樣嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6a8bfdccf983340c63c3a7435f08935cd5d1bc1","tid":1395141,"uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"你夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2287684cd682f48d8d33bd75aa89a6a89aeae530","tid":1395141,"uid":251052,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b6a8bfdccf983340c63c3a7435f08935cd5d1bc1","tid":1395141,"uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"你夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:09:37.000Z","msg":"我唔夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1e837cb80e9a009a95e98eb7ce8a4163711299","tid":1395141,"uid":24265,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:12:31.000Z","msg":"憑連衛兵<br />\n唔表態就係狗 就係支持 奶共<br />\n<br />\n屌人唔表態好撚弱智<br />\n<br />\n利申 未睇過達狗"},{"pid":"c4b2a8a41eb954e058f657015e059a928581c22a","tid":1395141,"uid":245670,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLidxzr.png\" data-thumbnai